data.description: **Price improvement**Welcome to this immaculate 2020-built townhome, cherished by its original owner. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, & a 2-car garage. The open floorplan seamlessly connects the beautiful kitchen, with pretty white cabinets, granite countertops, premium stainless appliances, to the spacious living area & dining area. Large primary bedroom with en-suite, with 2 additional bedrooms upstairs. Finished backyard with pavers is perfect for outdoor enjoyment. Situated in a gated community with a pool and play area, near freeways, Costco, & grocery stores, this townhome ensures convenience. Experience the allure of a nearly-new home that combines elegance, urban convenience, and community amenities.
